<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>hr_lite demo</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f4f5f7;
           color: #111827; margin: 0; display: grid; place-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
    .card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 14px; padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 26rem; width: calc(100% - 2rem); }
    h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 0 0 .25rem; }
    p { color: #6b7280; font-size: .9rem; }
    form { margin: .5rem 0; }
    button { width: 100%; min-height: 48px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
             border-radius: 9px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #fff; }
    button.primary { background: #2563eb; border-color: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
    small { color: #6b7280; display: block; margin-top: 1rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>hr_lite demo</h1>
    <p>Pick a persona — each sees a different tier of the HR portal.</p>
    <% @personas.each do |user| %>
      <%= button_to user.name, "/demo/sign_in/#{user.id}", method: :post,
            class: (user.email.include?("lead") ? "primary" : nil) %>
    <% end %>
    <small>Data resets every time you restart <code>bin/demo</code>.</small>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
